ast.name: Map My Trip
ast.comment: Uncertain which of your friends you should pick up first?  Not sure what order is best to run your errands in?  Map My Trip is your solution!  Map My Trip will take the places you need to go to and find the best order to go to them in! #PurdueHackathon
